WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:03.190
Wow, that was fast.

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.910
Well, good evening everybody. Thank you

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:09.750
for joining us tonight. I

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.830
don't know where Braden wants to go from

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.549
here. I've got my microphone, but I had

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:19.029
a really interesting conversation

00:00:19.039 --> 00:00:21.670
yesterday on the phone.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:27.750
Every year, I evaluate where we are,

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:29.910
what the Lord has done, and what we could

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:32.310
do better. Especially now that we're

00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:36.549
in ministry, I

00:00:36.549 --> 00:00:36.559
evaluate

00:00:36.559 --> 00:00:38.310
the intimacy level—checking your

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:41.110
thermostat, as I call it. Where

00:00:41.110 --> 00:00:41.120
is

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:43.750
your thermostat with God? How

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:45.510
are things? If you were to get your

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:47.750
report card or your evaluation

00:00:47.750 --> 00:00:47.760
at

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:49.910
work

00:00:49.910 --> 00:00:49.920
for

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:51.830
how you did for the

00:00:51.830 --> 00:00:51.840
year—your

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:54.150
review for the

00:00:54.150 --> 00:00:54.160
year—and

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:57.430
the boss comes in and says,

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.110
'Well, you could have done this

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:01.189
better, or you did this

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:03.510
really well, and your progress report was

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:05.030
pretty good, so we'll give you a raise

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:06.789
or keep you

00:01:06.799 --> 00:01:09.910
where you are.'I go over things

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:11.830
with the Father like that all the time at the

00:01:11.830 --> 00:01:11.840
end of the

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:13.830
year.

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:16.310
I always evaluate and write

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.469
things down because I don't want

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:22.390
to be where I am at this time next year.

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:24.630
I look and see if I made any

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:26.870
progress spiritually.

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:29.429
After I had a really interesting

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:31.590
conversation with a

00:01:31.590 --> 00:01:31.600
mega-minister

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:33.990
yesterday—he

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.069
called and

00:01:36.079 --> 00:01:39.030
wanted to talk to me—I asked

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:40.789
some questions that I normally don't

00:01:40.799 --> 00:01:42.950
ask,

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:45.670
but the Lord told

00:01:45.670 --> 00:01:45.680
me to

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:47.749
ask him because he would have

00:01:47.759 --> 00:01:50.550
the answers.

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:55.670
I asked about a lot of

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:56.789
mega-prophets

00:01:56.799 --> 00:02:00.149
and how

00:02:00.159 --> 00:02:02.069
come they didn't sustain in ministry or

00:02:02.069 --> 00:02:02.079
why

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:05.510
they went home early.

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:07.510
I asked what happened to

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:09.830
some of these prophetic voices that

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:15.030
have gone before us. He went over

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:18.070
the details of why some of

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:22.150
these

00:02:22.160 --> 00:02:25.589
major voices that used to be—that are

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:27.430
no more—fell,

00:02:27.430 --> 00:02:27.440
and

00:02:27.440 --> 00:02:29.670
why their

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:31.910
ministries faltered.

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:33.750
He knew a lot of the

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:36.229
answers. As we were talking,

00:02:36.239 --> 00:02:39.750
it really bothered me.

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:44.949
One person was

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:50.949
messed up with homosexuality.

00:02:54.640 --> 00:02:58.790
One was messing around with

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:01.270
golden idols. There

00:03:01.270 --> 00:03:01.280
were

00:03:01.280 --> 00:03:03.750
so many different things.

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:08.390
As I heard it all,

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:10.949
I paused. They

00:03:10.959 --> 00:03:14.149
all started out really good

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:15.670
with great

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:17.670
intentions and great intimacy with

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.350
the Father.

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:22.229
You don't get there without intimacy.

00:03:22.239 --> 00:03:25.670
But what went wrong?

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:26.949
I'm not going to reveal these

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:30.630
men's names, but as I was thinking

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:32.949
about people I had looked up to

00:03:32.949 --> 00:03:32.959
and

00:03:32.959 --> 00:03:35.350
admired, you see

00:03:35.350 --> 00:03:35.360
the

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:37.350
slow

00:03:37.350 --> 00:03:37.360
fade

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:39.030
after year

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:42.710
after year of

00:03:42.710 --> 00:03:42.720
ministry.

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:45.030
I didn't get the answer right

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:48.949
off. I

00:03:48.959 --> 00:03:51.030
was praying all last night

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:54.710
and

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:56.470
seeking the Lord because of the

00:03:56.480 --> 00:04:00.070
things He's showing me.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:02.309
As you're checking your thermostat

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:05.509
of where you are with the Father, you

00:04:05.519 --> 00:04:07.990
have to ask, 'How is my

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:11.429
relationship with

00:04:11.429 --> 00:04:11.439
God?'I

00:04:11.439 --> 00:04:13.429
don't ever want to be

00:04:13.439 --> 00:04:14.949
arrogant and say, 'That will never happen

00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:17.990
to me,'because these people, in my opinion,

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.870
were the best over the years.

00:04:20.880 --> 00:04:25.030
How do you stay on the

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:27.830
right road? How do you self-evaluate?

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:40.230
I woke up this morning and the Lord

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:43.030
spoke to me in my sleep.

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:45.909
He said,

00:04:45.919 --> 00:04:50.150
'Intimacy is what gets you there

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:52.950
with Me, and intimacy is what will keep

00:04:52.960 --> 00:04:55.350
you

00:04:55.350 --> 00:04:55.360
there.'So

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:57.270
many times, these

00:04:57.280 --> 00:04:58.870
ministers start with healings,

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:00.070
demonstrations, and

00:05:00.080 --> 00:05:03.670
manifestations,

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:05.749
but they lose the intimacy with the

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:09.110
Father. The gift is separate from

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:11.909
intimacy. Intimacy is how you got the

00:05:11.919 --> 00:05:17.510
gift, but it's not how you sustain it.

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:20.950
Over

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:22.710
time,

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:24.469
you get so caught

00:05:24.469 --> 00:05:24.479
up—because

00:05:24.479 --> 00:05:27.830
it's trying to happen to

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:30.070
me—with

00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:33.510
the pulling on the gift

00:05:33.510 --> 00:05:33.520
that

00:05:33.520 --> 00:05:35.909
you believe

00:05:35.919 --> 00:05:38.310
walking underneath that mantle

00:05:38.310 --> 00:05:38.320
is

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:42.310
intimacy for the day.

00:05:45.039 --> 00:05:46.950
You're so busy with all the people

00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:49.510
pulling on you that you

00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:51.189
don't separate

00:05:51.199 --> 00:05:54.070
yourself to have the

00:05:54.080 --> 00:05:55.909
intimacy that got the gift in the first

00:05:55.919 --> 00:05:58.070
place.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:01.590
It becomes robotic.

00:06:01.600 --> 00:06:04.150
The Lord said, 'Brandon, it's a slow

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:05.990
fade.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:08.309
Many of the ministers you were told

00:06:08.319 --> 00:06:11.270
about yesterday started out just

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:15.350
like

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:17.110
you—on

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:20.950
fire and effective.

00:06:20.960 --> 00:06:24.230
But the gift and callings of God are

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:26.629
without

00:06:26.629 --> 00:06:26.639
repentance.'You

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:29.110
can

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:32.230
operate in a gift while there is stuff

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:34.150
going on in your personal life because

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:37.590
the gift is without repentance.

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:41.110
You qualify for it,

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:44.309
but if you cut yourself off the

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:46.469
vine, you

00:06:46.469 --> 00:06:46.479
don't

00:06:46.479 --> 00:06:49.270
die

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:51.830
instantaneously.

00:06:57.440 --> 00:07:02.950
Intimacy keeps you on the vine.

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:05.749
You cannot let

00:07:05.759 --> 00:07:11.270
intimacy with the Father die,

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:13.430
or eventually,

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:15.350
your ministry will be

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:17.909
short-lived.

00:07:17.919 --> 00:07:20.230
You cannot

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:22.710
rely just on the experience of

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:24.469
healings and demonstrations.

00:07:24.479 --> 00:07:26.390
I

00:07:26.400 --> 00:07:28.150
always tell you that covering comes on

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:30.309
me and I can feel it when I'm praying,

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:36.070
but

00:07:36.080 --> 00:07:38.390
the Lord was warning me: just because

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:39.990
you have that

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:42.469
impartation at that time doesn't mean

00:07:42.479 --> 00:07:45.029
you're

00:07:45.039 --> 00:07:46.950
walking in intimacy with Me.

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:48.390
You have to check your

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:51.270
spiritual thermostat. They

00:07:51.270 --> 00:07:51.280
are

00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:55.110
two different things.

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.629
He's been talking to me

00:07:56.639 --> 00:08:00.950
about evaluating your progress report.

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:11.189
I'm real open about

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:14.390
things, and I learn as I go. Some

00:08:14.390 --> 00:08:14.400
of the

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:16.790
elders

00:08:16.790 --> 00:08:16.800
who

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:18.869
went before us,

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:21.350
like Jack

00:08:21.350 --> 00:08:21.360
Coe,

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:22.790
were

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:24.309
warned about their weight.

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:26.550
He

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:29.510
was in his 30s when he passed

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:31.430
away.

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:35.110
What a tragic thing for somebody who

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:37.670
walked in so much creative miracles

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:40.310
to only have a ministry last until

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:45.269
their 30s.

00:08:55.760 --> 00:08:58.470
This is so taxing,

00:08:58.470 --> 00:08:58.480
with

00:08:58.480 --> 00:09:03.509
so much

00:09:03.519 --> 00:09:07.829
demand.

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:21.269
If you keep going down the

00:09:21.269 --> 00:09:21.279
road—because

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:23.350
some people were

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:25.030
committing adultery

00:09:25.030 --> 00:09:25.040
or

00:09:25.040 --> 00:09:27.110
were homosexual—the Lord

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:28.389
warned them, 'If you keep going down

00:09:28.399 --> 00:09:32.949
this road, you're going to

00:09:32.949 --> 00:09:32.959
hell.'The

00:09:32.959 --> 00:09:35.110
word of the Lord came up so

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:37.269
strong about this stuff that it

00:09:37.279 --> 00:09:40.070
shook me.

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:43.910
I even knew a man personally

00:09:46.230 --> 00:09:46.240
who

00:09:47.839 --> 00:09:50.070
was messing around on his wife for

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:51.829
two years prior to getting caught.

00:09:51.839 --> 00:09:53.430
The only reason he got caught was a

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:57.430
text message.

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:08.470
People ask how he

00:10:08.470 --> 00:10:08.480
kept

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:10.630
preaching. He said

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:14.790
the word is truth

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:16.630
regardless. So I'm just preaching the

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:19.590
word. It's okay; I knew that if

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:22.069
I could just keep preaching the word, it

00:10:22.079 --> 00:10:23.590
didn't matter about my personal life

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.190
because the word always stands by

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:27.590
itself. I believe that was it, wasn't

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:27.990
it?

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:31.190
And I was just thinking that is such a

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:34.310
dangerous place to be. But just going

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:38.470
over your year for 2025 and going

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:42.710
into 2026 and looking at what God has

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:45.590
for you so that you take what you did

00:10:45.590 --> 00:10:45.600
well

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:48.069
into the year and strip off the bad things.

00:10:48.079 --> 00:10:51.110
And the Lord told me,

00:10:51.120 --> 00:10:52.790
'Brandon, I've warned and warned

00:10:52.800 --> 00:10:54.310
my

00:10:56.240 --> 00:10:59.750
people.'It

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:03.910
keeps stirring up inside of me, what the Lord told me to

00:11:03.910 --> 00:11:03.920
say about 2026 and 1 Corinthians 5:5.

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:07.990
As I lay there this morning

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:11.030
and listened

00:11:11.040 --> 00:11:14.389
to the Father, I said, 'God,

00:11:14.399 --> 00:11:18.230
help me. Search me, know me, create in

00:11:18.240 --> 00:11:20.069
me a clean heart. Strip all this stuff

00:11:20.079 --> 00:11:23.350
off. Whatever it takes, intimacy

00:11:23.350 --> 00:11:23.360
with

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:26.230
Me is more important than anything

00:11:26.230 --> 00:11:26.240
else.

00:11:26.240 --> 00:11:29.350
Who cares if the

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:32.550
platform pulls you away from the Father?

00:11:32.550 --> 00:11:32.560
If

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:34.069
you're so

00:11:34.079 --> 00:11:36.470
distracted with the platform, then

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:39.750
it's time to prune it.

00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:43.670
Does that make sense? He's first.

00:11:43.680 --> 00:11:46.310
Intimacy is everything to have a

00:11:46.310 --> 00:11:46.320
relationship—the

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:47.990
fellowship that got you there in the

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:51.110
first place—to sustain it. That's

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:54.630
where dryness comes in.

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:56.310
There's so much dryness. I see

00:11:56.320 --> 00:11:57.829
pastors teaching out of

00:11:57.839 --> 00:12:01.030
their dryness and there's no good word.

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:03.269
I

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:05.350
even talked to one man and he said,

00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:07.269
'It's interesting. I can

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:10.550
go into a service and they're still

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:12.629
preaching on something that they were

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:15.190
preaching

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:18.310
30 years ago.

00:12:18.310 --> 00:12:18.320
Thirty

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:20.069
years later, they

00:12:20.079 --> 00:12:21.990
don't have any new wine or new

00:12:21.990 --> 00:12:22.000
wineskins,

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:25.590
continually

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:27.910
preaching the same

00:12:27.910 --> 00:12:27.920
thing.'You

00:12:27.920 --> 00:12:29.590
get to the point where you

00:12:29.590 --> 00:12:29.600
ask,

00:12:29.600 --> 00:12:32.069
'Do you not have any fresh

00:12:32.069 --> 00:12:32.079
Rhema

00:12:32.079 --> 00:12:34.150
from

00:12:34.160 --> 00:12:35.829
God?'Now,

00:12:35.839 --> 00:12:38.389
I know Brother Hagin taught

00:12:38.399 --> 00:12:41.829
Mark 11:23-24, but there was an anointing

00:12:41.839 --> 00:12:44.710
on it when he preached it.

00:12:44.720 --> 00:12:46.629
You could feel the tangible presence of

00:12:46.639 --> 00:12:48.949
God when he taught that. So obviously,

00:12:48.959 --> 00:12:51.350
in those cases, it was meant for

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:52.550
him to preach. Now, for some of these

00:12:52.550 --> 00:12:52.560
other

00:12:52.560 --> 00:12:55.110
people, it's like

00:12:55.120 --> 00:12:57.030
going into the Mojave Desert and

00:12:57.030 --> 00:12:57.040
wondering,

00:12:57.040 --> 00:12:59.750
'Why am I even

00:12:59.750 --> 00:12:59.760
here?'It's

00:12:59.760 --> 00:13:02.310
interesting when you talk to

00:13:02.320 --> 00:13:04.629
people who have been through the

00:13:04.639 --> 00:13:07.269
trenches, like the person I talked to

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:11.750
yesterday and another

00:13:11.760 --> 00:13:14.310
one of my mentors. It's been

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:16.550
interesting, the people who have called.

00:13:16.560 --> 00:13:21.269
You get to meditate on

00:13:21.279 --> 00:13:23.269
these things and walk

00:13:23.279 --> 00:13:26.069
away thinking, 'I don't want to say

00:13:26.079 --> 00:13:28.470
I'll never do that.'I always want to

00:13:28.480 --> 00:13:31.190
self-evaluate and be

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:33.509
humble about it. I'm not saying I'm better than

00:13:33.519 --> 00:13:36.470
them; heavens, no. For some of these

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:37.829
people, I couldn't even tie their

00:13:37.839 --> 00:13:39.509
shoelaces.

00:13:39.519 --> 00:13:42.310
But if you

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:44.310
don't self-evaluate your relationship

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:46.150
and look at your thermostat with God,

00:13:46.160 --> 00:13:48.629
you'll drift off easily. Just

00:13:48.639 --> 00:13:50.470
because you have a call and

00:13:50.480 --> 00:13:52.710
there's a mantle or

00:13:52.710 --> 00:13:52.720
an

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:55.590
impartation on that call doesn't mean

