00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:13.509
Am I pleasing to

00:14:13.509 --> 00:14:13.519
you?'After

00:14:13.519 --> 00:14:17.509
I sat and wept on the floor,

00:14:17.519 --> 00:14:19.910
He gave me a word. That word was

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:24.069
intimacy. It was private for me, but I'm

00:14:24.079 --> 00:14:26.790
very thankful for where I am with my

00:14:26.800 --> 00:14:28.310
Father.

00:14:28.320 --> 00:14:30.230
Yes, there are things you can work

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:34.150
