00:15:02.399 --> 00:15:04.949
true source.

00:15:04.959 --> 00:15:08.710
I realized as I listened

00:15:08.710 --> 00:15:08.720
that

00:15:08.720 --> 00:15:10.710
I don't want to be a statistic in

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:12.550
ministry.

00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:15.670
So as I focus on what

00:15:15.680 --> 00:15:18.389
