I try to be a place of

00:15:47.040 --> 00:15:49.030
refreshing for all people to come and

00:15:49.040 --> 00:15:52.470
drink from, so that when they are

00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:54.790
here, they get a fresh touch from the

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:57.829
Holy Ghost. The only way you can

00:15:57.839 --> 00:16:01.269
give—'Silver

00:16:01.279 --> 00:16:03.509
and gold have I none, but such as

00:16:03.519 --> 00:16:05.990
I have give I thee: In the name of Jesus

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:07.910
Christ of Nazareth rise up and

00:16:07.910 --> 00:16:07.920
walk'—is through

00:16:07.920 --> 00:16:10.870
intimacy. They had been

00:16:10.880 --> 00:16:13.829
with Jesus. They were unlearned,

00:16:13.839 --> 00:16:16.470
uneducated men who had been

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:18.550
with Jesus. That's what the Bible says.

00:16:18.560 --> 00:16:22.310
The world marveled

00:16:22.320 --> 00:16:25.350
