00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:28.150
It's not just being with Him

00:16:28.150 --> 00:16:28.160
once;

00:16:28.160 --> 00:16:30.870
it's being with Him continually, sitting

00:16:30.880 --> 00:16:33.829
at His feet. It's the intimacy with the

00:16:33.839 --> 00:16:37.189
Father that says, 'Jesus, I'm here. I

00:16:37.199 --> 00:16:39.030
need You to change me and take me from

00:16:39.040 --> 00:16:41.749
glory to glory.'In Diana's and my

00:16:41.749 --> 00:16:41.759
case, we

00:16:41.759 --> 00:16:43.670
practice what we preach

00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:43.680
when

00:16:43.680 --> 00:16:46.870
we say we walk in love—sowing

00:16:46.870 --> 00:16:46.880
even when

00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:48.870
