00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:05.429
them or be mean;

00:17:05.429 --> 00:17:05.439
you

00:17:05.439 --> 00:17:07.510
walk in love. When you

00:17:07.510 --> 00:17:07.520
sow,

00:17:07.520 --> 00:17:09.429
you give your

00:17:09.439 --> 00:17:11.750
