00:17:35.840 --> 00:17:37.430
want you to

00:17:37.430 --> 00:17:37.440
stay,'and

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:41.190
you keep working things out,

00:17:41.190 --> 00:17:41.200
it

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:44.789
makes your flesh scream. If your

00:17:44.799 --> 00:17:46.549
flesh isn't screaming, you aren't growing

00:17:46.559 --> 00:17:48.870
spiritually.

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:51.350
You need to know this. When He says

00:17:51.350 --> 00:17:51.360
to

00:17:51.360 --> 00:17:55.110
clean toilets for years,

00:17:55.120 --> 00:17:56.470
do it with a good

00:17:56.470 --> 00:17:56.480
heart—without

00:17:56.480 --> 00:17:59.750
grumbling and

00:17:59.760 --> 00:18:02.150
complaining.

00:18:02.160 --> 00:18:05.029
Live in a shotgun house for 20

00:18:05.039 --> 00:18:07.830
years. Do what I've asked

00:18:07.840 --> 00:18:09.669
without grumbling and

00:18:09.679 --> 00:18:11.590
complaining. Do all that you do, in

00:18:11.600 --> 00:18:13.909
word and

00:18:13.909 --> 00:18:13.919
deed,

00:18:13.919 --> 00:18:15.669
to the glory of God, and He'll

00:18:15.679 --> 00:18:18.070
release you.

00:18:18.080 --> 00:18:23.750
Do it with a joyful heart.

00:18:23.760 --> 00:18:26.870
The willing and obedient

00:18:26.880 --> 00:18:28.310
will eat the good of the

00:18:28.320 --> 00:18:31.430
land, not the grudging.

00:18:31.430 --> 00:18:31.440
There are

00:18:31.440 --> 00:18:33.110
so many times the Lord tells Diana

00:18:33.110 --> 00:18:33.120
and me

00:18:33.120 --> 00:18:34.630
to do something against our

00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:37.029
flesh. He says, 'I want you to sow

00:18:37.029 --> 00:18:37.039
this.'I think,

00:18:37.039 --> 00:18:40.470
'Are you kidding me?'But then

00:18:40.470 --> 00:18:40.480
I say,

00:18:40.480 --> 00:18:43.830
