00:18:50.950 --> 00:18:50.960
I

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:52.950
do it with

00:18:52.960 --> 00:18:54.870
a cheerful attitude and

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:56.870
walk in love.

00:18:56.880 --> 00:18:58.070
This

00:18:58.080 --> 00:19:01.110
happens to me all the time. The Lord

00:19:01.120 --> 00:19:03.990
says, 'This is molding you. If you do

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:06.470
what I tell you, you'll go to the

00:19:06.480 --> 00:19:08.710
next level. I'm

00:19:08.720 --> 00:19:11.830
watching your heart.'In a vision, I saw

00:19:15.120 --> 00:19:19.590
a path of white;

00:19:19.600 --> 00:19:22.870
it was beautiful but

00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:25.350
