00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:31.909
I pulled

00:19:31.919 --> 00:19:33.270
out of it because it freaked me out.

00:19:35.280 --> 00:19:37.029
I had to meditate on

00:19:37.029 --> 00:19:37.039
it

00:19:37.039 --> 00:19:39.029
because the Lord was dealing

00:19:39.039 --> 00:19:42.789
