00:19:46.960 --> 00:19:50.549
side of a mouth. His face

00:19:50.559 --> 00:19:53.510
was right on the edge of the path, but

00:19:53.520 --> 00:19:57.029
his eye was all I could see. I

00:19:57.039 --> 00:20:00.630
didn't say this, but he spoke to me in an

00:20:00.640 --> 00:20:02.310
audible voice in my house. That's why

00:20:02.320 --> 00:20:04.630
it freaked me out. I heard it. And

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:11.350
he says, 'I'm watching you.

00:20:11.360 --> 00:20:13.669
I'm watching you.'And that's why I

00:20:13.679 --> 00:20:16.230
started singing His Eye Is on the Sparrow,

00:20:16.240 --> 00:20:18.870
for I know he watches me. That's why I

00:20:18.880 --> 00:20:21.590
