00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:24.310
'I'm watching you, Brandon.

00:20:24.320 --> 00:20:26.470
I'm watching you and how you make these

00:20:26.480 --> 00:20:29.669
decisions and these choices. Do

00:20:29.679 --> 00:20:33.590
you qualify to go to the next level?

00:20:33.600 --> 00:20:37.270
Do you qualify to get more?

00:20:37.280 --> 00:20:39.909
I have more in store in 2026. I have

00:20:39.919 --> 00:20:41.590
more in store in the days

00:20:41.590 --> 00:20:41.600
