00:20:41.600 --> 00:20:45.190
do you qualify for it?

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:48.390
What qualifies you?

00:20:48.400 --> 00:20:50.230
Obedience.

00:20:50.240 --> 00:20:53.270
Listening whenever your flesh screams.

00:20:53.280 --> 00:20:55.750
Will you qualify, ladies and gentlemen,

00:20:55.760 --> 00:20:59.990
for what God has for you by obedience?

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:01.830
Obedience is better than sacrifice. And

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:04.630
it's not always easy when he tells you...

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:06.630
when people call and say,

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:08.549
'I got another call yesterday to go to

00:21:08.559 --> 00:21:10.230
