whatever, with hundreds of millions

00:23:28.880 --> 00:23:31.190
in the bank, whatever TV program.

00:23:31.200 --> 00:23:33.990
Listen, folks, I'm

00:23:33.990 --> 00:23:34.000
just

00:23:34.000 --> 00:23:37.350
into him. The byproduct of

00:23:37.360 --> 00:23:40.470
following him is blessing. I get that.

00:23:40.480 --> 00:23:43.029
But where I'm at right now is I want

00:23:43.039 --> 00:23:45.350
that anointing so strong that whenever

00:23:45.360 --> 00:23:48.470
people see it, they see Jesus in me and

00:23:48.480 --> 00:23:51.430
they say, 'Brandon,

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:55.350
what must I do to be saved?

00:23:55.360 --> 00:23:58.630
What must I do to be

00:23:58.630 --> 00:23:58.640
saved?'I

00:23:58.640 --> 00:24:02.470
am so broken that when

00:24:02.470 --> 00:24:02.480
my

00:24:02.480 --> 00:24:06.230
shadow passes by,

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:07.830
