of me,'but inside you're just weak with

00:25:45.279 --> 00:25:47.590
arrogance? Because I see some people,

00:25:47.600 --> 00:25:49.669
they take pictures with their Gucci

00:25:49.679 --> 00:25:51.110
pants and they've got their stuff on there

