01:04:31.520 --> 01:04:33.990
sister Lyn Hammond. She is a living word

01:04:34.000 --> 01:04:36.150
up in Minnesota. And I listened to these

01:04:36.160 --> 01:04:38.150
tapes over and over. My mom got them at

01:04:38.160 --> 01:04:40.230
a convention and I listened to them over

01:04:40.240 --> 01:04:41.349
and over again. And I said,

01:04:41.359 --> 01:04:42.710
"Father, I want to learn how to pray

01:04:42.720 --> 01:04:45.510
like this,

01:04:45.510 --> 01:04:45.520
too."I

01:04:45.520 --> 01:04:47.349
was praying and my brother and I

01:04:47.349 --> 01:04:47.359
shared

01:04:47.359 --> 01:04:49.910
bunk beds. And the power of God hit my

01:04:49.920 --> 01:04:53.510
head with fire

01:04:53.520 --> 01:04:57.510
and my ears and my head felt like I

01:04:57.520 --> 01:04:59.670
was on fire and I started seeing the

01:04:59.680 --> 01:05:01.670
spirit for the first time. And I saw

01:05:01.680 --> 01:05:04.150
a major vision and I didn't know what I

01:05:04.160 --> 01:05:07.190
was seeing and it freaked me out. So I

01:05:07.200 --> 01:05:09.029
ran out of the room and I told my mom

01:05:09.039 --> 01:05:10.630
and my dad, I said, "Listen, this is

01:05:10.640 --> 01:05:13.510
what I'm seeing."And I told

01:05:13.520 --> 01:05:15.750
them, we lived in Fort Worth, Texas at

01:05:15.760 --> 01:05:18.390
the time. My mom

01:05:18.400 --> 01:05:20.150
and dad were going to Jerry

01:05:20.150 --> 01:05:20.160
Savelle's

01:05:20.160 --> 01:05:21.990
Bible School.

01:05:22.000 --> 01:05:25.349
And that was my first vision.

01:05:25.359 --> 01:05:28.870
I was working at Albertson's.

01:05:28.880 --> 01:05:31.029
I sacked groceries.

01:05:32.880 --> 01:05:35.750
So I learned how to pray and do all that

01:05:35.760 --> 01:05:37.990
then. And then I started working at a

01:05:38.000 --> 01:05:40.789
ministry and I started listening to

01:05:40.799 --> 01:05:43.270
them, how to pray, and the Lord

01:05:43.280 --> 01:05:45.109
said, "I'm going to give you mantels to

01:05:45.109 --> 01:05:45.119
pray."And

01:05:45.119 --> 01:05:48.069
then the Reinhard

01:05:48.069 --> 01:05:48.079
Bonnke

01:05:48.079 --> 01:05:52.069
came to a staff meeting. And Reinhard

01:05:52.069 --> 01:05:52.079
Bonnke

01:05:52.079 --> 01:05:54.390
called people and said, "Do you

01:05:54.400 --> 01:05:56.870
want to—I feel in my heart to pray

01:05:56.880 --> 01:05:59.670
for people."And whenever he came to

01:05:59.680 --> 01:06:01.750
me, he said, the Lord said, he said,

01:06:01.760 --> 01:06:03.349
"I'm going to put a double portion of

01:06:03.359 --> 01:06:07.510
the anointing on my life on

01:06:07.510 --> 01:06:07.520
you."And

01:06:07.520 --> 01:06:10.470
he laid hands on me. And the power

01:06:10.480 --> 01:06:13.190
of God knocked me on my

01:06:13.190 --> 01:06:13.200
hindy.

01:06:13.200 --> 01:06:15.430
And I felt electricity go through my

01:06:15.440 --> 01:06:17.829
body when Reinhard Bonnke prayed for

01:06:17.839 --> 01:06:19.990
me. I can even tell you where I was

01:06:20.000 --> 01:06:23.270
standing. I was standing on the

01:06:23.280 --> 01:06:25.190
left-hand

01:06:25.200 --> 01:06:28.789
side of the stage. I walked up

01:06:28.799 --> 01:06:31.029
where it was by the baptismal area and

01:06:31.039 --> 01:06:32.230
there were so many people wanting to go

01:06:32.240 --> 01:06:33.829
up to the front to get prayed for. And

01:06:33.839 --> 01:06:36.470
when he laid his hands on me, the

01:06:36.480 --> 01:06:38.710
fire of God went through my body and

01:06:38.720 --> 01:06:40.549
whenever that all happens, everything

01:06:40.559 --> 01:06:43.029
started changing with me.

01:06:43.039 --> 01:06:44.710
That's when things really started taking

01:06:44.720 --> 01:06:49.829
off after Reinhard Bonnke prayed for me.

01:06:49.839 --> 01:07:09.190
If anybody knows who Reinhard Bonnke is.

01:07:09.200 --> 01:07:11.589
And so then another part of it was when

01:07:11.599 --> 01:07:13.190
I went to another meeting in Fort

01:07:13.200 --> 01:07:14.710
Lauderdale, Florida, there was a man

01:07:14.720 --> 01:07:17.190
named Ralph Wilkerson.

01:07:17.200 --> 01:07:19.990
He had Melodyland Christian Center and

01:07:20.000 --> 01:07:22.390
he was with Kathryn Kuhlman. And he saw

01:07:22.400 --> 01:07:24.390
me and he gave me a prophetic word

01:07:24.400 --> 01:07:27.109
and he said, "God has put his

01:07:27.119 --> 01:07:29.430
hand on you and you have the same kind

01:07:29.440 --> 01:07:31.829
of a mantle like Kathryn

01:07:31.829 --> 01:07:31.839
Kuhlman

01:07:31.839 --> 01:07:33.750
and

01:07:33.760 --> 01:07:37.270
another man."And he said, "I

01:07:37.280 --> 01:07:39.349
want to lay hands on your hands and he

01:07:39.359 --> 01:07:41.190
said, there's an impartation of a double

01:07:41.200 --> 01:07:44.390
portion on my life on you."So he put

01:07:44.400 --> 01:07:46.789
his hands on my hands and the fire of

01:07:46.799 --> 01:07:49.510
God hit my hands like a matchstick. And

01:07:49.520 --> 01:07:50.870
I can still feel it every once in a

01:07:50.880 --> 01:07:53.029
while. I don't feel it very often, but

01:07:53.039 --> 01:07:54.470
whenever it does, I lay hands on people

01:07:54.480 --> 01:07:56.950
and they get healed. Now the Lord

01:07:56.960 --> 01:07:58.470
has recently been talking to me about it

01:07:58.480 --> 01:08:00.789
again and saying that there's

01:08:00.799 --> 01:08:02.150
something major fixing to happen with

01:08:02.160 --> 01:08:04.230
this, but it's only been in

01:08:04.240 --> 01:08:07.270
spurts. But when it comes on, like I

01:08:07.280 --> 01:08:08.789
told you about the boy's face, other

01:08:08.799 --> 01:08:10.870
people and angels come in and they

01:08:10.880 --> 01:08:12.950
minister to the people around me. But

01:08:12.960 --> 01:08:15.750
that has not happened a lot. What the

01:08:15.760 --> 01:08:18.390
man that got brand new lungs,

01:08:18.400 --> 01:08:20.470
things like that, but it's only been

01:08:20.480 --> 01:08:22.390
progressive. And when I touched the dogs

01:08:22.400 --> 01:08:24.709
and they raised the dogs from the dead,

01:08:24.719 --> 01:08:26.550
when the dogs came back

01:08:26.560 --> 01:08:29.829
from the dead, that was amazing. But

01:08:29.839 --> 01:08:32.470
I've only seen that big creative

01:08:32.480 --> 01:08:33.990
miracles like that happen like four or

01:08:34.000 --> 01:08:37.110
five. Well, what is it? More than that.

01:08:37.120 --> 01:08:38.789
It's been several times 'cause I laid hands

01:08:38.799 --> 01:08:41.110
on Diana on something. Power of God

01:08:41.120 --> 01:08:42.309
went to her and she was completely

01:08:42.319 --> 01:08:43.669
healed immediately. And that was really

01:08:43.679 --> 01:08:47.189
cool when it happened for my wife.

01:08:47.199 --> 01:08:49.669
But that was after Ralph Wilkerson

01:08:49.679 --> 01:08:51.269
prayed for me.

01:08:51.279 --> 01:08:52.870
And they're Oral Roberts. So other than

01:08:52.880 --> 01:08:55.269
that,

01:08:55.279 --> 01:08:57.349
you know, I try—you know, it's like

01:08:57.359 --> 01:08:59.669
what do you do with that? You know,

01:08:59.679 --> 01:09:02.149
they're just men. I'm thankful for every

01:09:02.159 --> 01:09:03.590
one of them. They're not—both of them

01:09:03.600 --> 01:09:06.229
are not here anymore. But I was thankful

01:09:06.239 --> 01:09:08.309
and grateful for the people who have

01:09:08.319 --> 01:09:10.870
prayed for me and were obedient

01:09:10.880 --> 01:09:13.590
to what the Lord called them to do.

01:09:13.600 --> 01:09:16.070
And so you just put it on a shelf until

01:09:16.080 --> 01:09:18.470
the Lord calls it out. I don't focus on

01:09:18.480 --> 01:09:21.430
it. I just keep praying and doing what

01:09:21.440 --> 01:09:23.349
he's asked me to do. Now, I know that

01:09:23.359 --> 01:09:28.550
there'll be more things happening for

01:09:28.560 --> 01:09:30.390
my ministry in the days ahead 'cause he

01:09:30.400 --> 01:09:32.229
told me this won't always be my ministry.

01:09:42.880 --> 01:09:46.229
What does intimacy with God look like?

01:09:46.239 --> 01:09:48.709
Oh, that's beautiful.

01:09:48.719 --> 01:09:51.189
Now, that's a good question.

01:09:51.199 --> 01:09:55.590
What does intimacy with God look like?

01:09:55.600 --> 01:09:58.390
Raw.

01:09:58.400 --> 01:10:02.070
It's not rehearsed.

01:10:02.080 --> 01:10:05.750
It's not religious.

01:10:05.760 --> 01:10:10.390
It's just vulnerable.

01:10:10.400 --> 01:10:12.950
Vulnerable is intimacy with the

01:10:12.960 --> 01:10:17.189
father. When you go to him just

01:10:17.199 --> 01:10:19.830
as you are,

01:10:19.840 --> 01:10:22.070
he knows everything that you're going to

01:10:22.080 --> 01:10:23.990
say before you're going to say it. So

01:10:24.000 --> 01:10:25.430
don't pretend that he doesn't know

01:10:25.440 --> 01:10:27.669
you're going to say it

01:10:27.679 --> 01:10:31.590
or be fake. He already knows

01:10:31.600 --> 01:10:34.310
you've had a bad day. He already knows

01:10:34.320 --> 01:10:36.790
if you're mad at him.

01:10:36.800 --> 01:10:39.189
So just be real.

01:10:39.199 --> 01:10:41.270
That's why I say out of intimacy with

01:10:41.280 --> 01:10:43.750
God, when you get real with God, God

01:10:43.760 --> 01:10:46.310
will become real to you.

01:10:46.320 --> 01:10:48.709
That's why he's real with me. I don't

01:10:48.719 --> 01:10:52.229
fake it. There are no 'thee's and 'thou's.

01:10:52.239 --> 01:10:55.030
It's not all this hype.

01:10:55.040 --> 01:10:58.470
I just go to him broken, and I lay before

01:10:58.480 --> 01:11:00.390
his feet

01:11:00.400 --> 01:11:04.229
and I picture myself there.

01:11:04.239 --> 01:11:07.430
I have an inward image of it,

01:11:07.440 --> 01:11:09.990
and I go there in my mind

01:11:10.000 --> 01:11:13.110
and I see him.

01:11:13.120 --> 01:11:14.870
And I know a lot of you say, 'Well, I

01:11:14.880 --> 01:11:16.310
can't go there because I've never had

01:11:16.320 --> 01:11:18.630
that before, Brandon. I don't have any

01:11:18.640 --> 01:11:22.390
vision of Jesus.'But I didn't either.

01:11:22.400 --> 01:11:25.430
I had it inside of my mind's eye. I

01:11:25.440 --> 01:11:27.270
pictured it even before I knew what he

01:11:27.280 --> 01:11:29.350
looked

01:11:29.350 --> 01:11:29.360
like—that

01:11:29.360 --> 01:11:32.070
I'm going before him bold. I've

01:11:32.080 --> 01:11:34.950
had a really crappy day

01:11:34.960 --> 01:11:36.790
and I'm going to him and I'm going to

01:11:36.800 --> 01:11:39.669
touch his garment and I'm not letting go

01:11:39.679 --> 01:11:44.870
until he blesses me.

01:11:44.880 --> 01:11:48.390
When you get that desperation

01:11:48.400 --> 01:11:52.229
like you need air, like you need food, and

01:11:52.229 --> 01:11:52.239
there is

01:11:52.239 --> 01:11:53.910
so much

01:11:53.920 --> 01:11:55.430
desperation, that's when the intimacy

01:11:55.440 --> 01:11:57.590
comes out of it.

01:11:57.600 --> 01:12:00.310
And a lot of my intimacy came

01:12:00.310 --> 01:12:00.320
because I

01:12:00.320 --> 01:12:02.470
was poor.

01:12:02.470 --> 01:12:02.480
We

01:12:02.480 --> 01:12:04.630
didn't have money to pay our bills.

01:12:04.640 --> 01:12:06.390
And I knew that they were going to cut my

01:12:06.390 --> 01:12:06.400
electricity

01:12:06.400 --> 01:12:09.590
off. And I was desperate to get

01:12:09.600 --> 01:12:12.229
my electric paid. When you're making

01:12:12.239 --> 01:12:14.870
hardly nothing and you're a janitor

01:12:14.880 --> 01:12:18.229
and you have a wife and kids

01:12:18.239 --> 01:12:19.990
and they're living on food

01:12:20.000 --> 01:12:22.470
stamps already, and you're looking at

01:12:22.480 --> 01:12:24.470
going and doing things and you don't

01:12:24.480 --> 01:12:27.430
have enough gas money to get to work, and

01:12:27.440 --> 01:12:30.229
you're thinking, 'How is this going to

01:12:30.239 --> 01:12:32.709
come to pass? I've got to find Jesus

01:12:32.719 --> 01:12:35.669
right

01:12:35.669 --> 01:12:35.679
now.'And

01:12:35.679 --> 01:12:39.189
my relationship was born out of a

01:12:39.199 --> 01:12:41.350
lot of pressure,

01:12:41.360 --> 01:12:44.470
a lot of pain, and a lot of hurt. Megan was

01:12:44.480 --> 01:12:46.950
diagnosed with autism

01:12:46.960 --> 01:12:50.310
and I felt like I was having a

01:12:50.320 --> 01:12:54.070
breakdown. And in that,

01:12:54.080 --> 01:12:56.950
he became real to me.

01:12:56.960 --> 01:12:59.430
It was in the toilet cleaning.

01:12:59.440 --> 01:13:01.350
It was in the window washing that

01:13:01.360 --> 01:13:04.470
Jesus became real to me because I just

01:13:04.480 --> 01:13:05.910
said, 'I'm doing everything I'm doing

01:13:05.920 --> 01:13:08.390
for you. And if you never use me at all

01:13:08.400 --> 01:13:11.270
and I just clean this glass, every time

01:13:11.280 --> 01:13:13.270
somebody comes in here, I want them to

01:13:13.280 --> 01:13:15.189
be able to look at these floors and want

01:13:15.199 --> 01:13:18.390
to be able to eat off of them. If they

01:13:18.400 --> 01:13:20.070
can look at this and they come

01:13:20.080 --> 01:13:22.149
in here and it's not a distraction to

01:13:22.159 --> 01:13:25.110
them, they come in here unsaved and it's

01:13:25.120 --> 01:13:26.229
not a distraction. They come in this

01:13:26.239 --> 01:13:27.669
bathroom and they go, "This is the

01:13:27.679 --> 01:13:29.590
stinkiest church bathroom I've ever seen

01:13:29.600 --> 01:13:32.470
in my life. The glass is out of control,

01:13:32.480 --> 01:13:35.430
the floors are all nasty, and I don't

01:13:35.440 --> 01:13:36.870
want to ever come back in here because

01:13:36.880 --> 01:13:40.390
these people are pigs."I thought, I don't

01:13:40.400 --> 01:13:43.189
want to be the cause of that. So, I made

01:13:43.199 --> 01:13:45.830
sure it was always the best it was.

01:13:45.840 --> 01:13:49.270
If Jesus was coming to church today,

01:13:49.280 --> 01:13:53.669
I want to make it look good for him.

01:13:53.679 --> 01:13:55.350
And that's the only way I can make

01:13:55.360 --> 01:13:58.790
it. I thought, if Jesus is coming... so I know

01:13:58.800 --> 01:14:00.550
when that Sister clipboard's is coming here

01:14:00.560 --> 01:14:06.149
and she's going to fuss about things,

01:14:06.159 --> 01:14:08.709
I'm going to make it look good for her that

01:14:08.719 --> 01:14:11.910
maybe she's had a hard week and we're

01:14:11.920 --> 01:14:13.350
going to make it look as nice as we can

01:14:13.360 --> 01:14:15.189
for them. And that's where the intimacy

01:14:15.189 --> 01:14:15.199
came

01:14:15.199 --> 01:14:18.870
out of.

01:14:18.880 --> 01:14:24.310
I drove a long way to work.

01:14:24.320 --> 01:14:25.830
Erica wants to go too, and she's like,

01:14:25.840 --> 01:14:27.910
'Shut up.

01:14:27.920 --> 01:14:29.990
Go turn whoever Eric is.'I look at the

01:14:30.000 --> 01:14:31.510
comments.

01:14:31.520 --> 01:14:34.470
So there you go. If that's

01:14:34.480 --> 01:14:36.070
what I can answer some questions for

01:14:36.080 --> 01:14:45.481
y'all.

01:14:45.491 --> 01:14:47.110
Sweet. She got prayed for by

01:14:47.120 --> 01:14:48.950
it. Do something with it. I like that she has a

01:14:48.960 --> 01:14:53.830
cowboy hat.

01:14:53.840 --> 01:14:57.271
Yeehaw! Mary, I love cowboy

01:14:57.271 --> 01:14:57.281
hats.

01:14:57.281 --> 01:14:59.750
You can go ride a horse. Let's

01:14:59.760 --> 01:15:08.407
see here.

01:15:14.640 --> 01:15:15.910
I'm

01:15:15.920 --> 01:15:18.229
concerned about New Madrid because I saw

01:15:18.239 --> 01:15:21.110
a lot of people die.

01:15:21.120 --> 01:15:24.070
A lot of the southern houses

01:15:24.080 --> 01:15:27.430
over here are built on cinder blocks.

01:15:27.440 --> 01:15:29.350
So they're not real stable on foundation

01:15:29.360 --> 01:15:31.990
homes. A lot of the houses around here

01:15:32.000 --> 01:15:34.229
are all built on these concrete blocks.

01:15:34.239 --> 01:15:36.310
So I don't know how good they would do

01:15:36.320 --> 01:15:39.270
with an 8.4 earthquake. Probably not

01:15:39.280 --> 01:15:48.362
real good.

01:15:50.000 --> 01:15:52.950
I like horses. I'm just

01:15:52.960 --> 01:15:55.510
scared because they're so big.

01:15:55.520 --> 01:15:56.870
My dad raised

01:15:56.870 --> 01:15:56.880
Longhorn

01:15:56.880 --> 01:15:59.510
cows and they'll butcher them

01:15:59.520 --> 01:16:01.510
and sell their meat,

01:16:01.520 --> 01:16:03.990
Longhorn meat,

01:16:04.000 --> 01:16:07.357
stuff like that.

01:16:07.367 --> 01:16:08.630
It's a pretty good deal on

01:16:08.640 --> 01:16:10.550
some organic beef. And that's true

01:16:10.560 --> 01:16:19.350
organic beef.

01:16:19.360 --> 01:16:20.950
I don't know if he's still doing that. I

01:16:20.960 --> 01:16:22.390
should say that before people go,

01:16:22.400 --> 01:16:23.990
"Where do I find that

01:16:23.990 --> 01:16:24.000
meat?"I

01:16:24.000 --> 01:16:26.870
don't want the emails.

01:16:26.880 --> 01:16:36.149
I know he does it.

01:16:36.159 --> 01:16:38.149
The Lord said you will not pray away the

01:16:38.159 --> 01:16:41.270
plague.

01:16:41.280 --> 01:16:43.189
The Lord said you will lessen the

01:16:43.199 --> 01:16:44.630
plague.

01:16:44.640 --> 01:16:47.110
And he said it will not affect you,

01:16:47.120 --> 01:16:48.310
believer, if you

01:16:48.320 --> 01:16:52.790
understand Psalm 91 and Psalm 23.

01:16:52.800 --> 01:16:54.470
He said, 'I will hide you in the

01:16:54.470 --> 01:16:54.480
cleft

01:16:54.480 --> 01:16:56.870
of my rock, but you will have to

01:16:56.880 --> 01:17:00.070
know the word, for hard days are

01:17:00.080 --> 01:17:01.910
coming.'That's

01:17:01.920 --> 01:17:04.390
what he said. Shaking to awaken

01:17:04.400 --> 01:17:08.229
is coming. You lessen it. I don't know

01:17:08.239 --> 01:17:10.709
what that means because I saw hundreds

01:17:10.719 --> 01:17:13.510
of millions of people dying.

01:17:13.520 --> 01:17:17.430
So that's why I come on here so

01:17:17.440 --> 01:17:19.669
intensely telling y'all you must

01:17:19.679 --> 01:17:21.990
understand who you are. You must

01:17:22.000 --> 01:17:24.390
understand your covenant. You must

01:17:24.400 --> 01:17:27.350
understand the believer's authority,

01:17:27.360 --> 01:17:29.830
Sister Billie Brim. And not just read it

01:17:29.840 --> 01:17:32.950
once, but I'm talking about having

