How do you sow to

01:45:31.990 --> 01:45:32.000
the thousand-year reign?

01:45:32.000 --> 01:45:34.550
How do you

01:45:34.550 --> 01:45:34.560
sow

01:45:34.560 --> 01:45:36.229
to

01:45:36.229 --> 01:45:36.239
the

01:45:36.239 --> 01:45:38.790
thousand-year

01:45:38.790 --> 01:45:38.800
reign?

01:45:38.800 --> 01:45:41.270
What do you mean, financially,

01:45:41.280 --> 01:45:43.350
to get a better position in

01:45:43.350 --> 01:45:43.360
the thousand-year

01:45:43.360 --> 01:45:46.229
reign? Do everything you do in word and

01:45:46.239 --> 01:45:50.149
in deed to the glory of God.

01:45:50.159 --> 01:45:54.790
If you are

01:45:54.800 --> 01:45:58.390
doing it for show—well, those who sow in

01:45:58.400 --> 01:46:00.550
private will reap openly.

01:46:04.800 --> 01:46:06.629
Everything you do, do unto God, but

01:46:06.639 --> 01:46:08.629
don't do it for man's praise. If you get

01:46:08.639 --> 01:46:10.310
praise here, you won't get praise

01:46:10.320 --> 01:46:12.790
there.

01:46:12.800 --> 01:46:16.629
You must do it when nobody is watching you

01:46:16.639 --> 01:46:19.109
and without wanting them to give you applause.

01:46:19.119 --> 01:46:21.350
If I got applause here, you

01:46:21.350 --> 01:46:21.360
aren't

01:46:21.360 --> 01:46:23.910
getting applause there; it's for the

01:46:23.920 --> 01:46:25.830
thousand years. I try to do

01:46:25.830 --> 01:46:25.840
everything—even the

01:46:25.840 --> 01:46:27.910
bathrooms.

01:46:27.920 --> 01:46:30.229
Do something that is really detested

01:46:30.229 --> 01:46:30.239
by

01:46:30.239 --> 01:46:32.149
your flesh. Maybe you

01:46:32.159 --> 01:46:33.830
don't like mowing the grass or pulling

01:46:33.840 --> 01:46:35.510
weeds; go do it for the church and don't

01:46:35.520 --> 01:46:37.590
ask for any kind of reward or tell

01:46:37.600 --> 01:46:39.990
anybody about it.

01:46:40.000 --> 01:46:41.510
"Look at me! I just want to let you

01:46:41.520 --> 01:46:43.590
all know I volunteered at the church and

01:46:43.600 --> 01:46:46.629
gave my time to the nursery."I want

01:46:46.639 --> 01:46:48.390
everybody to know I was special at

01:46:48.400 --> 01:46:50.070
the nursery and

01:46:50.080 --> 01:46:52.550
did all this for free for the last 10

01:46:52.560 --> 01:46:54.790
years.

01:46:54.800 --> 01:46:56.950
Don't tell

01:46:56.950 --> 01:46:56.960
anybody;

01:46:56.960 --> 01:46:59.750
I did it for Jesus.

01:46:59.760 --> 01:47:02.070
I picked up the trash in the parking

01:47:02.080 --> 01:47:05.669
lot and did it for Him. I was the golf

01:47:05.679 --> 01:47:07.590
cart guy that brought people up from

01:47:07.600 --> 01:47:11.270
the front when it was cold. I was out

01:47:11.280 --> 01:47:13.830
there waving my stick, parking

01:47:13.840 --> 01:47:15.990
cars when it was freezing, but I didn't

01:47:16.000 --> 01:47:19.109
ask for praise from anybody. Or I gave

01:47:19.119 --> 01:47:21.590
this to the homeless guy on the side

01:47:21.600 --> 01:47:23.189
of the road and didn't have my camera

01:47:23.199 --> 01:47:24.950
out so I could put it on social media

01:47:24.960 --> 01:47:27.910
how great I was:

01:47:27.920 --> 01:47:29.669
"Look at this guy, he's really

01:47:29.679 --> 01:47:31.590
hurting. Let me get him some McDonald's.

01:47:31.600 --> 01:47:33.109
Oh, brother, aren't you having a hard

01:47:33.109 --> 01:47:33.119
time?"And

01:47:33.119 --> 01:47:34.229
they're filming it and

01:47:34.239 --> 01:47:35.830
putting it on YouTube to get

01:47:35.840 --> 01:47:37.350
likes, subscribers, and

01:47:37.360 --> 01:47:39.030
comments. It's

01:47:39.040 --> 01:47:40.790
baloney.

01:47:40.800 --> 01:47:42.950
Do it without having people tell you how

01:47:42.960 --> 01:47:45.109
great you are. Who cares?

01:47:45.119 --> 01:47:48.070
Deflect.

01:47:48.080 --> 01:47:50.390
The more you deflect and bring

01:47:50.400 --> 01:47:53.109
the glory to Him, doing it out of humility rather than pride, the more

01:47:58.159 --> 01:48:00.550
you'll get rewarded in

01:48:00.560 --> 01:48:02.599
the

01:48:02.609 --> 01:48:09.510
thousand-year

01:48:09.520 --> 01:48:12.470
reign.

01:48:12.470 --> 01:48:12.480
It's

01:48:12.480 --> 01:48:13.990
sad; they don't teach that

01:48:14.000 --> 01:48:16.550
at church because people don't know what the

01:48:16.560 --> 01:48:36.229
thousand years is.

01:48:36.239 --> 01:48:41.830
So

01:48:41.840 --> 01:48:44.310
yes, still the weird twilight and

01:48:44.320 --> 01:48:46.709
the birds.

01:48:46.719 --> 01:48:48.550
Brandon, do you remember the weird

01:48:48.560 --> 01:48:50.790
twilight, the birds, and the deer acting

01:48:50.800 --> 01:48:53.990
different? The breeding patterns? I

01:48:54.000 --> 01:48:55.750
still think about that.

01:48:55.760 --> 01:48:57.830
Something is going to happen with the sun.

01:48:57.840 --> 01:48:59.270
There's going to

01:48:59.270 --> 01:48:59.280
be

01:48:59.280 --> 01:49:02.310
some kind of haze over the Earth's

01:49:02.320 --> 01:49:05.270
atmosphere. I saw

01:49:05.270 --> 01:49:05.280
that

01:49:05.280 --> 01:49:07.830
the animals and the migrations in

01:49:07.840 --> 01:49:10.790
the days ahead will be altered.

01:49:10.800 --> 01:49:12.470
They'll start breeding when they're not

01:49:12.480 --> 01:49:14.709
supposed to. For example, the rut for

01:49:14.719 --> 01:49:17.270
deer in Oklahoma is usually in November,

01:49:17.280 --> 01:49:20.470
but I saw them starting to breed and

01:49:20.480 --> 01:49:22.470
having the rut in September. That

01:49:22.480 --> 01:49:27.030
throws off the babies when they're born;

01:49:27.040 --> 01:49:29.030
you want spring babies, not winter

01:49:29.040 --> 01:49:31.270
babies.

01:49:31.280 --> 01:49:35.189
It's dangerous for the mama

01:49:38.310 --> 01:49:38.320
deer.

01:49:40.080 --> 01:49:43.189
I saw the birds migrating too

01:49:43.199 --> 01:49:45.990
early. I saw a haze and it

01:49:45.990 --> 01:49:46.000
messed

01:49:46.000 --> 01:49:49.350
with people's minds—you know

01:49:49.360 --> 01:49:52.070
how people overcome

01:49:52.070 --> 01:49:52.080
sadness?

01:49:52.080 --> 01:49:54.709
I saw the fog; it made the

01:49:54.719 --> 01:49:58.149
plants stop growing right

01:49:58.159 --> 01:50:00.550
and

01:50:00.560 --> 01:50:02.790
threw the cycle of

01:50:02.800 --> 01:50:09.590
life off.

01:50:09.600 --> 01:50:12.149
No

01:50:12.159 --> 01:50:16.870
boasting. Keep your boasting to none.

01:50:16.880 --> 01:50:20.070
You have to seek Jesus

01:50:20.080 --> 01:50:21.830
without having people tell you how great

01:50:21.840 --> 01:50:24.070
you are. Jesus

01:50:24.070 --> 01:50:24.080
is

01:50:24.080 --> 01:50:36.149
great.

01:50:41.040 --> 01:50:43.910
Do I think college is worth it?

01:50:43.920 --> 01:50:46.070
It depends. Diana has a Master's

01:50:46.080 --> 01:50:49.510
degree. She graduated Summa

01:50:49.510 --> 01:50:49.520
Cum Laude.

01:50:49.520 --> 01:50:51.350
She graduated

01:50:51.360 --> 01:50:53.590
top of her class for both

01:50:53.600 --> 01:50:55.590
her Bachelor's and her Master's

01:50:55.590 --> 01:50:55.600
and

01:50:55.600 --> 01:51:00.790
is

01:51:00.800 --> 01:51:03.910
still the smartest person

01:51:03.920 --> 01:51:06.390
I've ever met. But

01:51:06.400 --> 01:51:09.189
she only uses it every once in a

01:51:09.199 --> 01:51:14.070
while.

01:51:14.080 --> 01:51:17.270
What is God telling you

01:51:17.280 --> 01:51:20.149
to do? Do you feel God has told you to

01:51:20.159 --> 01:51:22.870
go to college? If you're

01:51:22.880 --> 01:51:25.510
doing it to make money, I would not do

01:51:25.520 --> 01:51:28.709
that. I would pursue God and ask Him

01:51:28.719 --> 01:51:30.550
what He wants to do with my life before

01:51:30.560 --> 01:51:32.550
I have some harebrained idea

01:51:32.550 --> 01:51:32.560
like,

01:51:32.560 --> 01:51:33.830
"I think I'm going to be

01:51:33.840 --> 01:51:36.390
an

01:51:36.390 --> 01:51:36.400
architect."Was

01:51:36.400 --> 01:51:39.030
that God? No, that's flesh. Everything

01:51:39.040 --> 01:51:41.589
you do, pray and fast and ask God what

01:51:41.599 --> 01:51:44.870
you're supposed to do. Now, will she use

01:51:44.880 --> 01:51:46.470
her degree in the future for our

01:51:46.480 --> 01:51:49.589
ministry? Yes. I know why God told her

01:51:49.599 --> 01:51:52.390
to do that now. Back then,

01:51:52.400 --> 01:51:54.229
I thought, "What in the

01:51:54.239 --> 01:51:56.470
world are we doing this for?"At the

01:51:56.480 --> 01:51:57.750
time, I thought we were doing church

01:51:57.760 --> 01:52:00.629
finances, but now our church is online.

01:52:00.639 --> 01:52:02.790
This is our church, and we're believing

01:52:02.800 --> 01:52:05.030
God for partners,

01:52:05.040 --> 01:52:06.709
but I've never asked for a

01:52:06.719 --> 01:52:09.430
dime. I know

01:52:09.440 --> 01:52:11.669
that eventually we'll have a

01:52:11.679 --> 01:52:13.910
congregation or a

01:52:13.910 --> 01:52:13.920
big ministry

01:52:13.920 --> 01:52:15.510
and she'll use it.

01:52:18.960 --> 01:52:21.990
We see what God is doing, and this

01:52:21.990 --> 01:52:22.000
has

01:52:22.000 --> 01:52:25.990
really taken off now. Do I feel that

01:52:26.000 --> 01:52:29.030
college is worth it? I personally

01:52:29.040 --> 01:52:30.310
think there are a lot of other things you

01:52:30.320 --> 01:52:32.470
can do to be an entrepreneur

01:52:32.470 --> 01:52:32.480
without

01:52:32.480 --> 01:52:34.629
going

01:52:34.639 --> 01:52:37.669
to school. It's

01:52:37.669 --> 01:52:37.679
a

01:52:37.679 --> 01:52:39.750
hard question.

01:52:39.760 --> 01:52:41.589
A lot of people feel if you don't get a good

01:52:41.599 --> 01:52:43.510
education, you won't get the better jobs

01:52:43.520 --> 01:52:46.229
and become CEOs.

01:52:46.229 --> 01:52:46.239
But

01:52:46.239 --> 01:52:47.750
you're talking to a guy who barely has

01:52:47.760 --> 01:52:55.109
a GED.

01:52:55.119 --> 01:52:56.709
I 70% agree with you.

01:53:01.840 --> 01:53:03.430
Trade schools are better investments.

01:53:03.440 --> 01:53:06.390
Learning a trade, like

01:53:06.390 --> 01:53:06.400
being

01:53:06.400 --> 01:53:09.143
a mechanic or

01:53:09.153 --> 01:53:10.149
an

01:53:10.159 --> 01:53:12.550
electrician, is

01:53:12.550 --> 01:53:12.560
a good

01:53:12.560 --> 01:53:15.189
idea. As

01:53:15.189 --> 01:53:15.199
I've said,

01:53:15.199 --> 01:53:17.990
you're talking to

01:53:18.000 --> 01:53:20.950
a man who

01:53:20.950 --> 01:53:20.960
has

01:53:20.960 --> 01:53:22.870
to really study even to

01:53:22.870 --> 01:53:22.880
read or do

01:53:22.880 --> 01:53:24.950
math.

01:53:24.960 --> 01:53:26.550
I would have loved to be smart

01:53:26.560 --> 01:53:28.709
like Diana and be a

01:53:28.719 --> 01:53:31.430
doctor or a lawyer,

01:53:31.440 --> 01:53:33.589
but God wanted me to do what

01:53:33.599 --> 01:53:35.350
I'm doing, and I'm thankful for what He

01:53:35.360 --> 01:53:39.189
has me doing now—praying with you and doing

01:53:39.199 --> 01:53:44.870
eBay and Poshmark.

01:53:44.880 --> 01:53:47.189
I saw the guy making

01:53:47.189 --> 01:53:47.199
arks.

01:53:47.199 --> 01:53:50.070
He's

01:53:50.080 --> 01:53:52.070
off. The Bible says that He will not

01:53:52.080 --> 01:53:54.629
flood the earth again. From what I understand, he's saying

01:53:54.639 --> 01:53:55.910
there's

01:53:55.920 --> 01:53:58.070
going to be a major flood again. There

01:53:58.080 --> 01:53:59.910
will be no major flood. God said

01:53:59.920 --> 01:54:03.030
He's going to judge the earth with fire.

01:54:03.040 --> 01:54:05.910
The Bible says that

01:54:05.910 --> 01:54:05.920
after

01:54:05.920 --> 01:54:08.149
the ark and

01:54:08.159 --> 01:54:09.830
the flood, He made the

01:54:09.840 --> 01:54:11.750
rainbow to promise He wouldn't flood the

01:54:11.760 --> 01:54:13.589
earth again. If you think the earth

01:54:13.599 --> 01:54:15.669
is going to be flooded again, you're not

01:54:15.679 --> 01:54:17.430
reading your Bible. The Bible

01:54:17.430 --> 01:54:17.440
says

01:54:17.440 --> 01:54:19.109
He's not flooding the earth again; the

01:54:19.119 --> 01:54:22.550
next time will be by fire.

01:54:22.560 --> 01:54:24.390
So don't build an ark saying God

01:54:24.390 --> 01:54:24.400
told

01:54:24.400 --> 01:54:25.830
you a flood's coming,

01:54:25.840 --> 01:54:26.950
because there isn't one coming.

01:54:26.960 --> 01:54:28.709
We'll have small floods, but

01:54:28.719 --> 01:54:30.149
He's not flooding the whole earth.

01:54:30.159 --> 01:54:32.709
That's not biblical.

01:54:32.719 --> 01:54:35.750
I think Bible college is a great idea. I

01:54:35.760 --> 01:54:37.750
would go to RU.

01:54:37.760 --> 01:54:41.830
I think OU is a great school to support,

01:54:41.840 --> 01:54:46.470
like

01:54:46.470 --> 01:54:46.480
Rhema.

01:54:46.480 --> 01:54:49.430
We sell things we find

01:54:51.520 --> 01:54:53.189
at thrift stores on eBay

01:54:53.189 --> 01:54:53.199
and Poshmark.

01:54:53.199 --> 01:54:55.270
We have relationships with

01:54:55.280 --> 01:54:57.430
thrift stores. You can sell anything

01:54:57.440 --> 01:54:59.189
on eBay, but I think anything you

01:54:59.199 --> 01:55:01.270
can put in a poly mailer is a good

01:55:01.280 --> 01:55:02.550
idea.

01:55:02.560 --> 01:55:04.310
Boxes are hard and take a lot of work

01:55:04.320 --> 01:55:08.390
to pack, but poly mailers are easy. Just drop the

01:55:08.390 --> 01:55:08.400
item

01:55:08.400 --> 01:55:10.709
in there and ship it off.

01:55:10.719 --> 01:55:12.470
We put a lot on there today;

01:55:13.119 --> 01:55:15.559
that was fun.

01:55:20.080 --> 01:55:30.070
I guess people like asking questions.

01:55:40.960 --> 01:55:42.950
I don't believe in Ozempic. The Lord told

01:55:42.950 --> 01:55:42.960
me to

01:55:42.960 --> 01:55:45.589
stay away from it. I was

01:55:45.599 --> 01:55:47.109
going to do it, but the Lord said no.

01:55:47.119 --> 01:55:50.070
If it helps you, that's

01:55:50.070 --> 01:55:50.080
fine,

01:55:50.080 --> 01:55:52.390
but I'm not a doctor

01:55:52.390 --> 01:55:52.400
and

01:55:52.400 --> 01:55:54.790
can't give medical advice.

01:55:54.800 --> 01:55:56.709
He told me personally not to take Ozempic,

01:55:56.709 --> 01:55:56.719
even though

01:55:56.719 --> 01:55:59.510
I'm always looking for a

01:55:59.520 --> 01:56:02.550
shortcut because I like food. Father,

01:56:02.560 --> 01:56:06.390
I thank You for the time we have

01:56:06.400 --> 01:56:08.229
right

01:56:08.239 --> 01:56:10.870
now. We're going to go tubing, and I

01:56:10.880 --> 01:56:13.990
dedicate this time to You. I'm sure

01:56:13.990 --> 01:56:14.000
some

01:56:14.000 --> 01:56:15.589
will be upset because it's

01:56:15.589 --> 01:56:15.599
been

01:56:15.599 --> 01:56:17.669
going for two hours, but we'll pray for a

01:56:17.679 --> 01:56:20.229
little bit; it doesn't matter.

01:56:20.239 --> 01:56:21.669
Father, I thank You for every

01:56:21.679 --> 01:56:23.510
question they have.

01:56:23.520 --> 01:56:25.350
Many people are hungry and

01:56:25.360 --> 01:56:27.350
desperate for answers.

01:56:27.350 --> 01:56:27.360
There aren't

01:56:27.360 --> 01:56:29.270
enough

01:56:29.280 --> 01:56:31.830
pastors who put themselves out there to

01:56:31.840 --> 01:56:35.430
answer the hard things. Lord, I try.

01:56:35.440 --> 01:56:37.189
I may not have all the answers, but

01:56:37.199 --> 01:56:39.270
I know what You've told me on some

01:56:39.280 --> 01:56:41.990
of it. I thank You that

01:56:42.000 --> 01:56:44.629
I do my best. Many people

01:56:44.639 --> 01:56:46.149
are looking for

01:56:46.159 --> 01:56:49.669
leadership in these last days. Father, I

01:56:49.679 --> 01:56:52.229
thank You that You raise up leaders with

01:56:52.239 --> 01:56:54.790
a backbone like a crowbar who do

01:56:54.800 --> 01:56:57.430
not sway from the hard things.

01:56:57.440 --> 01:56:58.950
Even if they don't know the

01:56:58.960 --> 01:57:00.390
answer, they can just say

01:57:00.390 --> 01:57:00.400
they

01:57:00.400 --> 01:57:01.750
don't know. Just like Kathryn

01:57:01.750 --> 01:57:01.760
Kuhlman said,

01:57:01.760 --> 01:57:02.950
'I don't have the answer for

01:57:02.950 --> 01:57:02.960
that.'It's

01:57:02.960 --> 01:57:06.149
okay to say, 'I don't

01:57:06.149 --> 01:57:06.159
know.'Billy

01:57:06.159 --> 01:57:07.830
tells me all the time, 'It's

01:57:07.840 --> 01:57:10.470
okay to say I don't

01:57:10.480 --> 01:57:14.950
know.'Father,

01:57:14.960 --> 01:57:18.149
we worship You.

01:57:32.719 --> 01:57:35.510
We sit at Your feet, Lord.

01:57:35.510 --> 01:57:35.520
What

01:57:35.520 --> 01:57:37.109
is

01:57:37.119 --> 01:57:38.709
happening on the earth right now

01:57:38.719 --> 01:57:41.589
with all these shootings and

01:57:41.589 --> 01:57:41.599
everything

01:57:41.599 --> 01:57:43.430
else?

01:57:43.440 --> 01:57:45.669
Father, is there more we can alert

01:57:45.679 --> 01:57:48.550
people to?

01:57:48.560 --> 01:57:53.270
You lead, we follow.

01:59:51.920 --> 01:59:52.550
Father, we

01:59:52.560 --> 01:59:55.990
call forth the rain

01:59:56.000 --> 02:00:01.430
over the area.

02:00:46.000 --> 02:00:48.070
He said, 'I'm taking you back to what I

02:00:48.080 --> 02:00:51.510
showed you several weeks

02:00:51.520 --> 02:00:55.510
ago.'The

02:00:55.520 --> 02:00:59.430
spinning of the

02:01:06.639 --> 02:01:08.870
black and yellow on the little

02:01:08.880 --> 02:01:11.910
hypnotic

02:01:11.920 --> 02:01:19.589
wheel.

02:01:19.599 --> 02:01:28.229
I see the United States flag.

02:01:28.239 --> 02:01:30.070
On the hypnotic

02:01:30.080 --> 02:01:32.709
wheel, it's black and yellow.

