02:40:01.840 --> 02:40:04.550
and a boy.

02:40:04.550 --> 02:40:04.560
The

02:40:04.560 --> 02:40:07.590
girl has red

02:40:07.600 --> 02:40:12.469
hair and fair

02:40:12.469 --> 02:40:12.479
