02:40:28.240 --> 02:40:30.630
I see the

02:40:30.630 --> 02:40:30.640
boy;

02:40:30.640 --> 02:40:33.990
he has oily

02:40:34.000 --> 02:40:37.830
brown hair and

02:40:37.830 --> 02:40:37.840
