02:40:47.200 --> 02:40:48.870
us.

02:40:48.880 --> 02:40:50.389
I can see them very

02:40:50.389 --> 02:40:50.399
clearly.

02:40:50.399 --> 02:40:51.670
They are

02:40:51.670 --> 02:40:51.680
saying,

02:40:51.680 --> 02:40:55.190
