02:40:55.200 --> 02:40:57.670
us.'I

02:40:57.680 --> 02:41:01.190
agree with you.

02:41:01.200 --> 02:41:04.070
Let the Lord lead you. There is a

02:41:04.080 --> 02:41:06.710
group of you gathering and praying, and the

02:41:06.710 --> 02:41:06.720
Lord is

02:41:06.720 --> 02:41:09.110
going to use you,

02:41:09.120 --> 02:41:10.790
but you have a lot of

02:41:10.800 --> 02:41:13.190
Pharisees around you—a lot of

02:41:13.200 --> 02:41:15.110
elders always trying

02:41:15.120 --> 02:41:19.670
