02:41:19.670 --> 02:41:19.680
devil.'But

02:41:19.680 --> 02:41:21.030
the Holy Ghost and fire are going to stir you.

02:41:21.030 --> 02:41:21.040
You have

02:41:21.040 --> 02:41:22.469
gotten some good

02:41:22.479 --> 02:41:24.469
teaching and there is a stirring in you; God

02:41:24.469 --> 02:41:24.479
is

02:41:24.479 --> 02:41:26.710
going to use you. I see old

02:41:26.720 --> 02:41:30.950
religious relics around you;

02:41:30.960 --> 02:41:37.990
it looks like a stone

02:41:40.790 --> 02:41:40.800
graveyard

02:41:45.359 --> 02:41:47.270
where Christians on fire come to

02:41:47.280 --> 02:41:49.750
die.

02:41:49.760 --> 02:41:55.750
But you are going to change that.

02:41:55.760 --> 02:41:57.190
I can hear

02:41:57.200 --> 02:42:00.070
it: 'This is where Christians on fire come to die.'In this area, if you are on

02:42:00.080 --> 02:42:03.830
fire, you

02:42:03.830 --> 02:42:03.840
do not

02:42:03.840 --> 02:42:05.510
stay on

02:42:05.520 --> 02:42:08.070
fire because

02:42:09.680 --> 02:42:18.389
of

02:42:21.520 --> 02:42:23.349
these people in black with

02:42:23.359 --> 02:42:36.870
rope belts,

02:42:36.870 --> 02:42:36.880
like monks.

02:42:36.880 --> 02:42:39.670
But the revival will start with you. He

02:42:39.680 --> 02:42:42.389
will use you for a great explosion of

02:42:42.399 --> 02:42:46.070
glory if you just yield.

02:42:46.070 --> 02:42:46.080
It is

02:42:46.080 --> 02:42:47.670
all hands on deck, ladies and

02:42:47.680 --> 02:42:49.830
gentlemen. I am telling you, He wants

02:42:49.840 --> 02:42:52.389
to do something huge in Ireland. He

02:42:52.389 --> 02:42:52.399
is

02:42:52.399 --> 02:42:54.230
talking about Ireland tonight.

02:42:54.240 --> 02:42:56.550
I can see your flag.

02:43:01.280 --> 02:43:04.950
He has not forgotten Ireland.

02:43:04.960 --> 02:43:06.870
It

02:43:06.880 --> 02:43:08.950
is

02:43:08.960 --> 02:43:11.030
not mentioned very much, not even

02:43:11.040 --> 02:43:13.270
in our materials. But the Lord said, 'I

02:43:13.280 --> 02:43:18.070
have not forgotten

02:43:18.070 --> 02:43:18.080
Ireland.'It

02:43:18.080 --> 02:43:30.230
seems very cold and damp with

02:43:30.230 --> 02:43:30.240
a

02:43:30.240 --> 02:43:33.190
demonic spirit over there,

02:43:33.200 --> 02:43:43.590
but you have authority over

02:43:43.590 --> 02:43:43.600
that—no

02:43:43.600 --> 02:43:58.389
more.

02:43:58.399 --> 02:44:02.150
I see meetings being held. Even

02:44:05.520 --> 02:44:07.429
the religious

02:44:07.439 --> 02:44:10.309
government will try to hush this and persecute you. But

02:44:10.309 --> 02:44:10.319
you

02:44:10.319 --> 02:44:12.950
will

02:44:12.960 --> 02:44:15.510
stand even in persecution, and

02:44:15.520 --> 02:44:17.990
people's lives will be changed. It will come

02:44:17.990 --> 02:44:18.000
even through persecution, but

02:44:18.000 --> 02:44:20.469
lives will

02:44:25.439 --> 02:44:29.510
change.

02:44:29.520 --> 02:44:32.389
I see a storm around it; it is trying to

02:44:32.399 --> 02:44:33.990
get you weary

02:44:33.990 --> 02:44:34.000
in

02:44:34.000 --> 02:44:35.510
well-doing.

02:44:35.520 --> 02:44:39.190
Should we just quit? No. He is going to

02:44:43.680 --> 02:44:45.990
breathe

02:44:46.000 --> 02:44:48.950
into you when the time gets even harder. I see a

02:44:48.960 --> 02:44:54.630
group of you

02:44:54.630 --> 02:44:54.640
with

02:44:54.640 --> 02:45:24.790
curly hair. You

02:45:24.790 --> 02:45:24.800
say,

02:45:24.800 --> 02:45:26.070
'We

02:45:26.080 --> 02:45:28.790
do

02:45:28.800 --> 02:45:31.110
not

02:45:31.120 --> 02:45:48.150
have any money,'but the Lord will provide.

02:45:48.160 --> 02:45:50.950
Glory to God.

02:45:50.960 --> 02:45:52.870
Father, I thank You. We just

02:45:52.870 --> 02:45:52.880
undergird

02:45:52.880 --> 02:45:54.710
these people. We pray for them

02:45:54.720 --> 02:45:57.510
right now that they will have boldness

02:45:57.520 --> 02:45:59.830
and

02:45:59.840 --> 02:46:03.190
not shy back. They

02:46:03.190 --> 02:46:03.200
will

02:46:03.200 --> 02:46:05.429
stand in the name of Jesus.

02:46:05.429 --> 02:46:05.439
When

02:46:05.439 --> 02:46:07.429
adversity comes against

02:46:07.439 --> 02:46:09.910
them, they will stand.

02:46:09.920 --> 02:46:11.670
I thank You, Father, that the glory of

02:46:11.680 --> 02:46:14.710
the Lord is on them

02:46:14.710 --> 02:46:14.720
and

02:46:14.720 --> 02:46:17.269
no weapon formed against

02:46:17.279 --> 02:46:19.030
them shall prosper;

02:46:19.040 --> 02:46:21.110
religious spirits flee when they see

02:46:21.120 --> 02:46:22.870
the fire,

02:46:22.880 --> 02:46:28.950
in the name of Jesus.

02:46:28.960 --> 02:46:31.190
Thank you, Father.

02:46:31.200 --> 02:46:32.870
Hallelujah.

02:46:32.880 --> 02:46:43.830
Thank you, Lord.

02:46:43.840 --> 02:46:46.630
Well, that was interesting.

02:46:58.880 --> 02:47:00.230
We prayed for three or four

02:47:00.240 --> 02:47:01.910
different places tonight, didn't we? We prayed for

02:47:01.920 --> 02:47:05.670
Guatemala, the Highlands, Cuba...

02:47:05.680 --> 02:47:08.389
we saw the spinning

02:47:09.279 --> 02:47:11.429
gyroscope again concerning the

02:47:11.439 --> 02:47:15.590
biological weapon. We saw Ireland,

02:47:15.600 --> 02:47:18.630
a volcano, and

02:47:18.630 --> 02:47:18.640
what

02:47:18.640 --> 02:47:20.389
looked like a plague at the beginning. There

02:47:20.389 --> 02:47:20.399
are

02:47:20.399 --> 02:47:21.910
a lot of things

02:47:21.920 --> 02:47:23.429
splintered in different ways:

02:47:23.439 --> 02:47:26.230
calling for the harvest, praying for

02:47:26.240 --> 02:47:29.670
David and his teams,

02:47:29.680 --> 02:47:32.230
praying for a major revival in the

02:47:32.240 --> 02:47:35.110
islands for Guatemala. He

02:47:35.110 --> 02:47:35.120
is

02:47:35.120 --> 02:47:37.349
talking about how the

02:47:37.359 --> 02:47:38.710
harvest is plentiful but the laborers are

02:47:38.720 --> 02:47:42.230
few.

02:47:50.720 --> 02:47:55.349
What I saw looked like the jungle in

02:47:55.349 --> 02:47:55.359
Guatemala. I

02:47:55.359 --> 02:47:58.070
saw a

02:47:58.070 --> 02:47:58.080
snake and

02:47:58.080 --> 02:48:00.790
things

02:48:00.800 --> 02:48:03.190
for

02:48:03.200 --> 02:48:05.349
drinking water

02:48:05.349 --> 02:48:05.359
in

02:48:05.359 --> 02:48:06.710
those mountains.

02:48:07.120 --> 02:48:09.990
Do people

02:48:10.000 --> 02:48:11.670
live out there? I have no idea, but

02:48:11.680 --> 02:48:13.190
these people look like hut

02:48:13.200 --> 02:48:15.510
people,

02:48:15.520 --> 02:48:19.510
not modern.

02:48:19.510 --> 02:48:19.520
Anyone

02:48:19.520 --> 02:48:21.910
drinking rainwater off a tree

02:48:21.920 --> 02:48:45.750
is not modern. I

02:48:45.750 --> 02:48:45.760
am

02:48:45.760 --> 02:48:49.030
tired.

02:48:49.030 --> 02:48:49.040
I

02:48:49.040 --> 02:48:50.790
am

02:48:50.800 --> 02:48:58.870
glad we started early tonight;

02:48:58.880 --> 02:49:00.469
I should not have answered so many

02:49:00.479 --> 02:49:03.110
questions,

02:49:03.120 --> 02:49:05.349
but it is different today. They

02:49:05.359 --> 02:49:07.110
were saying that in your tongues, you

02:49:07.110 --> 02:49:07.120
were speaking

02:49:07.120 --> 02:49:09.590
about volcanoes in the water in Spanish. I

02:49:09.590 --> 02:49:09.600
said

02:49:09.600 --> 02:49:10.710
maremoto,

02:49:10.710 --> 02:49:10.720
which

02:49:10.720 --> 02:49:12.870
means 'seaquake.'That

02:49:12.870 --> 02:49:12.880
is

02:49:12.880 --> 02:49:14.070
what you were saying.

02:49:17.279 --> 02:49:19.349
I was seeing an earthquake and lots of

02:49:19.359 --> 02:49:22.230
volcanoes.

02:49:22.240 --> 02:49:23.910
Two people said that is what

02:49:23.920 --> 02:49:27.510
it meant.

02:49:30.560 --> 02:49:32.230
So, maremoto, huh?

02:49:39.200 --> 02:49:41.110
Volcanoes and a lot

02:49:41.110 --> 02:49:41.120
of fire;

02:49:41.120 --> 02:49:44.630
I saw

02:49:44.640 --> 02:49:47.030
the island and the people had

02:49:47.040 --> 02:49:54.150
nowhere to

02:49:54.160 --> 02:50:26.623
go—a

02:50:26.633 --> 02:50:29.670
seaquake.

02:50:29.680 --> 02:50:32.309
We thank You, Father, for showing us

02:50:32.309 --> 02:50:32.319
what

02:50:32.319 --> 02:50:33.990
is to come. He said, 'This is

02:50:34.000 --> 02:50:35.429
coming; it isn't here

02:50:35.439 --> 02:50:36.630
yet.

02:50:38.479 --> 02:50:39.670
You're seeing the

02:50:39.680 --> 02:50:46.630
future.'I

02:50:46.640 --> 02:50:48.150
saw the plague and people

02:50:48.160 --> 02:50:51.030
burning bodies.

02:50:51.040 --> 02:50:52.630
There were so many dead; it looked

02:50:52.640 --> 02:50:56.630
like a big arched fire pit. It was

02:50:59.680 --> 02:51:02.070
gross, but I couldn't see

02:51:02.080 --> 02:51:04.070
the bodies.

02:51:04.080 --> 02:51:05.670
You don't know the desperation of

02:51:05.670 --> 02:51:05.680
what

02:51:05.680 --> 02:51:06.710
is

02:51:06.710 --> 02:51:06.720
coming.

02:51:06.720 --> 02:51:07.990
He said

02:51:10.150 --> 02:51:10.160
it's

02:51:13.760 --> 02:51:19.510
sugarcoated Christianity.

02:51:19.520 --> 02:51:21.750
It's time for the church to preach

02:51:21.760 --> 02:51:25.030
the truth, the fire of the Holy Ghost. You must

02:51:25.040 --> 02:51:26.950
know your authority. You must know the

02:51:26.960 --> 02:51:28.790
power of the authority of the believer

02:51:28.800 --> 02:51:31.910
in the days ahead. People say, 'Oh well,

02:51:31.920 --> 02:51:33.830
we're not going to see

02:51:33.830 --> 02:51:33.840
anything.'You're

02:51:33.840 --> 02:51:38.309
blind as a bat. You must know the power

02:51:38.319 --> 02:51:42.710
and the authority of the believer

02:51:42.720 --> 02:51:45.190
by meditating on the word of God. Get

02:51:45.200 --> 02:51:46.790
the word of God down inside of your

02:51:46.800 --> 02:51:48.950
heart. Let it change you from the inside

02:51:48.960 --> 02:51:50.710
out.

02:51:50.720 --> 02:51:53.510
You must know and have authority and

02:51:53.520 --> 02:51:55.349
walk in it, lay hands on the sick and

02:51:55.359 --> 02:51:58.309
see them recover, cast out devils, and raise

02:51:58.319 --> 02:52:00.710
the dead. You have that power and

02:52:00.720 --> 02:52:02.389
authority on you. You're wall-to-wall

02:52:02.399 --> 02:52:04.389
Holy Ghost.

02:52:04.399 --> 02:52:05.590
Don't worry about everything else. God

02:52:05.600 --> 02:52:07.110
will provide for you. He'll take care of

02:52:07.120 --> 02:52:10.070
you and it will be fine.

02:52:10.070 --> 02:52:10.080
I'm

02:52:10.080 --> 02:52:12.070
telling you all, I saw a major

02:52:12.080 --> 02:52:14.389
revival come to Ireland, but

02:52:14.399 --> 02:52:17.190
the Lord is focused on calling

02:52:17.200 --> 02:52:19.990
the laborers in

02:52:20.000 --> 02:52:28.230
tonight.

02:52:28.240 --> 02:52:31.510
Father, we just thank you,

02:52:31.520 --> 02:52:33.190
Lord. I

02:52:33.200 --> 02:52:35.910
know I probably talked way too long,

02:52:35.920 --> 02:52:38.150
Lord,

02:52:38.160 --> 02:52:40.150
but we're so grateful, Father, for

02:52:40.160 --> 02:52:41.750
all the time we prayed for the people

02:52:41.760 --> 02:53:13.030
that we did.

02:53:13.040 --> 02:53:28.630
Light the torch.

02:54:07.439 --> 02:54:15.190
We thank you, Lord.

02:54:15.200 --> 02:54:16.710
We thank you, Lord, as you're stirring

02:54:16.720 --> 02:54:19.990
in our hearts today that we walk away,

02:54:20.000 --> 02:54:23.110
Father, with this uplifted and ready to

02:54:23.120 --> 02:54:25.990
conquer our day, Father, for this is the

02:54:26.000 --> 02:54:28.550
day that you have made and we will

02:54:28.560 --> 02:54:31.590
rejoice and be glad in it.

02:54:31.600 --> 02:54:34.710
And everybody say amen and amen.

02:54:34.720 --> 02:54:37.429
I had such a pull toward the people

02:54:37.439 --> 02:54:40.309
down there in Guatemala, that area. It

02:54:40.319 --> 02:54:43.030
looks so shady where they were. And then

02:54:43.040 --> 02:54:49.590
whenever I went to

02:54:49.600 --> 02:54:53.910
Ireland, it looked so damp and wet

02:54:53.920 --> 02:55:00.469
where these people were. It looked cold,

02:55:00.479 --> 02:55:02.550
very cold. And they

02:55:02.560 --> 02:55:05.030
didn't have money.

02:55:05.040 --> 02:55:07.590
I could see a house and I

02:55:07.600 --> 02:55:09.190
could see out their window. They had a

02:55:09.200 --> 02:55:12.790
window where they were praying.

02:55:12.800 --> 02:55:14.870
It looked like an apartment or some kind

02:55:14.880 --> 02:55:24.309
of place.

02:55:24.319 --> 02:55:26.230
Do you see that? It looked just

02:55:26.240 --> 02:55:30.469
something like that.

02:55:30.479 --> 02:55:34.150
That's exactly like that.

02:55:34.160 --> 02:55:36.150
That's neat that you'd pull up that.

02:55:36.160 --> 02:55:38.230
It

02:55:38.240 --> 02:55:42.630
looked like it was cold and dreary.

02:55:56.720 --> 02:55:59.349
God bless them. Thank you, Lord,

02:55:59.359 --> 02:56:00.950
that you stirred these people. You bring

02:56:00.960 --> 02:56:03.349
a fire in them.

02:56:03.359 --> 02:56:07.510
Set a fire down in my soul that I can't

02:56:07.520 --> 02:56:11.190
contain, that I can't control. I want

02:56:11.200 --> 02:56:13.990
more of you, God.

02:56:27.359 --> 02:56:29.269
Thank you, Father.

02:56:29.279 --> 02:56:31.190
Well, thank you for joining us tonight,

02:56:31.200 --> 02:56:33.750
folks. I know it was

02:56:33.750 --> 02:56:33.760
a

02:56:33.760 --> 02:56:36.469
three-hour long video. I talked way too

02:56:36.479 --> 02:56:38.070
long at the beginning

02:56:38.080 --> 02:56:39.750
answering questions. We should have

